;An Important Change in Firefox: Dedicated Profiles
Jun nïm Jaloj pa Firefox: K'aqöl Ruwäch B'i'aj


;What’s Changed
Achike Xjalatäj


;Before, all Firefox installations were sharing a single profile by default. Now, Firefox provides dedicated profiles for each Firefox installation (this includes installations of Firefox Nightly, Firefox Beta, or Firefox ESR). This will make Firefox more stable when switching between Firefox installations on the same computer.
Nab'ey, ronojel ri taq ruyakoj Firefox kikomonin xa jun ruwäch b'i'aj achi'el k'o wi. Wakami ri Firefox yeruya' ruwäch taq b'i'aj chi ke jujun ruyakoj Firefox ( re nutz'aqatisaj yakoj richin Firefox Nightly, Firefox Beta, o Firefox ESR). Re re' xtub'än chi yalan jikïl ri Firefox toq nuk'ëx chi kikojol ruyakoj Firefox pa jun kematz'ib'.


;How Dedicated Profiles Work
Achike rub'eyal yesamäj ri Samajel Ruwäch taq B'i'aj


;Firefox saves information such as bookmarks, passwords and user preferences in a set of files called your profile. This profile is stored in a separate location from the Firefox program files.
Firefox yeruyäk taq etamab'äl achi'el taq yaketal, ewan taq tzij chuqa' taq rajowab'al okisanel pa jun molaj yakb'äl kib'ina'am ruwäch ab'i'. Re ruwäch b'i'aj re' niyak pa jun chik k'ojlib'äl chi kiwäch ri taq ruyakb'al rukema' Firefox.


;The installation you choose as your primary Firefox installation will keep your previously shared profile data like bookmarks, history and passwords.
Ri yakoj nacha' achi'el nïm ayakoj richin Firefox xtuk'waj ri rutzij ruwäch ab'i', akomonin pan ajowab'äl, natab'äl chuqa' ewan tzij.


;You have not lost any personal data or customizations. Any previous profile data is safe and attached to the first Firefox installation that was opened after this change.
Man asachon ta majun awetamab'al o taq ichinanem. Xab'achike etamab'äl pa ruwäch ab'i' jikïl chuqa' tz'aqatisan rik'in ri nab'ey ruyakoj Firefox, ri xjaq chuwäch re jaloj re'.


;All of your Firefox installations will now have separate profiles.
Ronojel ri taq ruyakoj Firefox wakami e k'o pa jachon ruwäch taq b'i'aj.


;What You Need to Do
Achike Nik'atzin Nawetamaj Nab'än


;If you do nothing, each installation will have a separate profile. This means your profile data will be different on each installation of Firefox.
We majun nab'än, jujun yakoj xtik'oje' jun jachon ruwäch rub'i'. Ri nuq'ajuj chi taq rutzij ruwäch ab'i' man e junam ta pa jujun ruyakoj Firefox.


;You can change which installation uses which profile using the profile manager. Directions on how to use the profile manager are available on <a href="%(support)s">this support page</a>.
Yatikïr najäl achike yakoj nrokisaj jun ruwäch b'i'aj rik'in nawokisaj ri runuk'samajel kiwäch b'i'aj. Ri taq rutzijoxik rub'eyal nokisäx ri runuk'samajel kiwäch b'i'aj e k'o pa <a href="%(support)s">re ruxaq tob'äl re'</a>.


;While profiles are now connected to each installation of Firefox, you can use your Firefox Account to keep them in sync. If you would like all of your profile data to be the same on all installations of Firefox, we recommend you sync all of your profiles with a Firefox Account.
Wakami ke ri taq ruwäch b'i'aj e'okinäq kik'in jujun taq ruyakoj Firefox, yatikïr nawokisaj ri Rub'i' Ataqoya'l richin Firefox richin ye'axïm. We nawajo' chi ronojel ri taq kitzij ruwäch ab'i' e junam pa ronojel kiyakoj Firefox, niqachilab'ej chawe chi ke'axima' ronojel ri taq ruwäch ab'i' rik'in jun Ataqoya'l richin Firefox.


;A Firefox Account is the easiest way to make your profiles consistent on all of your versions of Firefox. You also get additional benefits like sending tabs and secure password storage.
Jun Rub'i' Ataqoya'l richin Firefox jun anin rub'eyal richin nab'än chi ri taq ruwäch ab'i' e junam pa ronojel ruwäch Firefox. Chuqa' nawïl rutz'aqat utzil achi'el ye'atäq taq ruwi' chuqa' ye'ayäk jeb'ël ri ewan taq atzij.


;You’re signed in and ready to start using Sync.
Xatikirisaj molojri'ïl chuqa' ütz chik nawokisaj ri Sync.


;We detected that you have installed and opened an older version of Firefox on your computer. You may need to take action.
Xqanab'ej chi xayäk chuqa' xajäq jun ojer ruwäch Firefox pan akematz'ib'. Rik'in jub'a' k'o chi k'o nab'än.


;We detected more than one version of Firefox on your computer. You may need to take action.
Xqanab'ej k'ïy taq ruwäch Firefox pan akematz'ib'. K'o chi k'o xtab'än.


